Installs and enables an apache
capable of http(s), ldap auth and DAV.
It depends on ldap_client being pulled in
(to bring the custom CA cert onto the machine).

For now, we use simple http namevhosts with logging,
serveraliases, server admin and a docroot.
Not exactly earth shattering, but already quite complex.

Needs a bit of a refactor and we can start on SSL, SVN repos etc.
